column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TRIDENT SPLASH GUM SPEARMINT 58.5 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000050098804
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sweeteners (maltitols, sorbitols, aspartame, acesulfame K), gum base, flavourings, humectant (glycerol), gelatine (bovine), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), colours (E171, E141), glazing agent (carnauba wax), thickener (E466). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine. Date available: 02/23/2018 Date last updated by company: 02/23/2018
